{
  "id": "69bd0eef059c1d33925e12ea",
  "title": "師弟歓談:私と小鳥とすずと",
  "created": 1773997810,
  "updated": 1773997904,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69bd0eef059c1d33925e12ea",
      "text": "師弟歓談:私と小鳥とすずと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997810,
      "updated": 1773997810
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1900000000009675c2",
      "text": "放課後の教室。窓の外で、小鳥がさえずっている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997850,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675c3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675c4",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675c5",
      "text": "「ねえ先生、『[私と小鳥とすずと]』ってさ、タイトルからしてエモくない？なんか“尊い”って感じするんだけど」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997872
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675c7",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675c8",
      "text": "「“尊い”というのは、心が動かされるほど大切で美しい、という意味でよろしいかしら。ええ、とてもやさしい響きの題ですね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675c9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675ca",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675cb",
      "text": "「そうそれ！でさ、“私”と“小鳥”と“すず”って並んでるけど、ぶっちゃけ何が言いたいの？って感じなんだよね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675cc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675cd",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675ce",
      "text": "「率直な疑問ですね。“結局、何を伝えたいのか分からない”というお気持ちかしら」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675cf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675d0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675d1",
      "text": "「そうそう、それそれ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675d2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675d3",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675d4",
      "text": "「この題は、それぞれ違う存在を並べているのが大切なのです。“私”は人間、“小鳥”は生き物、“すず”は物。けれど、どれも同じように大切だと感じる心を表しているのですよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675d5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675d6",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675d7",
      "text": "「え、でもさ、人とモノが同列って、なんかバグってない？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675d8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675d9",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675da",
      "text": "「“バグっている”というより、“境目をやわらかくしている”と考えるとよいでしょう。私たちは、つい価値に上下をつけてしまいがちですが、この考え方はそれを手放そうとしているのです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675db",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675dc",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675dd",
      "text": "「あー…なんか“みんな違ってみんないい”的なやつ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675de",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675df",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675e0",
      "text": "「ええ、とても近い表現ですね。ただ、“違うからこそ良い”だけでなく、“違っていても同じように愛おしい”という感覚でしょうか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675e1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675e2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675e3",
      "text": "「なるほどね…小鳥は生きてるし、すずはただの物だけど、どっちも“好き”って思える気持ちは同じってこと？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675e5",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675e6",
      "text": "「その通りです。好きだと感じる心に、厳密な区別はないのです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675e7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675e8",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675e9",
      "text": "「でもさ、正直言うと、テストとかでこういうの出ると“正解どれ？”ってなって詰むんだけど」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675eb",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675ec",
      "text": "「ふふ、“詰む”というのは、“どう答えてよいか分からなくなる”という意味ですね。そういうときは、“自分がどう感じたか”を大切にしてみてください」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675ed",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675ee",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675ef",
      "text": "「え、自分の感想でいいの？それズルじゃね？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675f0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675f1",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675f2",
      "text": "「“ズル”ではありませんよ。文学は、答えを当てるものではなく、感じるものですから」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675f4",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675f5",
      "text": "「へぇ〜…なんか意外。もっとガチガチに正解あると思ってたわ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675f7",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675f8",
      "text": "「もちろん、基本的な理解は大切ですけれどね。でも最後は、“あなたの心がどう動いたか”が一番大事なのです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675f9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675fa",
      "text": "（窓の外で、小鳥がひときわ高く鳴く）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675fb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675fc",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675fd",
      "text": "「…あ、なんか今ちょっと分かったかも。小鳥の声とか、こういう放課後の感じとかも、全部まとめて“いいな”って思う感じ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675fe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b00000000009675ff",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967600",
      "text": "「ええ、それこそが、“私と小鳥とすずと”の世界かもしれませんね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967601",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967602",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967603",
      "text": "「なんかさ、こういうのって、地味にじわるね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967604",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967605",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967606",
      "text": "「“じわる”というのは、“あとからゆっくりと心に響く”ということかしら。ええ、とても素敵な言い方ですね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967607",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967608",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967609",
      "text": "「でしょ？先生も使っていいよ、じわる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b000000000096760a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b000000000096760b",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b000000000096760c",
      "text": "「ありがとうございます。でも私は、やはり“しみじみと心に沁みる”と申しておきましょう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b000000000096760d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b000000000096760e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b000000000096760f",
      "text": "「うわ、急に品がすごい（笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967610",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967611",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967612",
      "text": "「ふふ、それが教師というものですよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967613",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967614",
      "text": "夕暮れが教室をやわらかく染める中、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
    },
    {
      "id": "69bd0f1b0000000000967615",
      "text": "ふーこは窓の外を見ながら、小さくつぶやいた。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773997851,
      "updated": 1773997851
